{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1682-02_189", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Air nouveau"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", février 1682 [tome 2], p. 189-191."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Rien n'est plus digne de suivre un Article si glorieux à la France, que les Paroles que je vous envoye. Tout est de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de Bassilly, qui les a faites à l'honneur du Roy. C'est ce qui luy arrive presque toûjours de composer l'un & l'autre ensemble. Il promet encor un Livre d´Airs qui sera gravé pour le mois de Mars,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Voir "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/ref[1]", "tag": "ref", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/ref[1]/text()[1]", "text": "cet article"}], "attributes": {"target": "MG-1682-06_083"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/text()[2]", "text": " qui annonce la parution effective de ce recueil et l'air de Bacilly "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Grand roi, quel bonheur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/note[1]/text()[3]", "text": "."}], "attributes": {"resp": "author", "place": "margin"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": " & qui fera connoistre au Public qu´il a toûjours le mesme génie pour le Chant, pour les Paroles, & pour les seconds Couplets en diminution. Ce Livre sera intitulé, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Second Mélange"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[4]", "text": ". Aucun des Airs qu'on y trouvera n'a encor paru, & les Connoisseurs à qui il a bien voulu les faire entendre, assûrent qu´il n´a jamais rien fait de si beau. Il est également fécond pour les Airs Sérieux, pour les Spirituels, pour les Bachiques, & les Chansonnetes. Son Livre de "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "l'Art de Chanter"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[5]", "text": " est dans une estime genérale. Aussi le voit-on cité en divers endroits dans celuy que le Pere Menestrier a mis au jour, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[4]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Des Représentations en Musique"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[6]", "text": ". Il a rendu justice par là à M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[5]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[5]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[7]", "text": " de Bassilly, quoy qu´il ne luy soit connu que par son Ouvrage."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "AIR NOUVEAU."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]", "tag": "note", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Avis pour placer les Figures"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/note[1]/text()[1]", "text": " : l’Air qui commence par Grand Roy, quel bonheur est le nostre, doit regarder la page 191."}], "attributes": {"resp": "author", "place": "margin"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Grand Roy, quel bonheur est le nostre,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "D'estre nez dans un temps où de nos propre yeux"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous voyons ce que nos Ayeux"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "N'ont jamais vû dans pas un autre !"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Nous devons plaindre ceux qui viendront apres nous."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils n'apprendront que par l'Histoire"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Vos exploits dont les Dieux mesmes seroient jaloux ; "}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Et ce qu'ils apprendront, ils ne le pourront croire."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/ref[1]", "tag": "ref", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/ref[1]/figure[1]", "tag": "figure", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/ref[1]/figure[1]/graphic[1]", "tag": "graphic", "children": [], "attributes": {"url": "images/1682-02_189.JPG"}}]}], "attributes": {"target": "images/1682-02_189.JPG"}}]}